transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Haan. Nikhil sir bol rahe hain?
Executive: Haan.
Customer: Nikhil sir, Shivam baat kar raha IndiaMART head office se manager.
Executive: Aapki aapne feedback diya tha like not getting any relevant leads ka and kuch din pehle hamari call bhi shayad schedule ki ho nahi payi thi. To may I know kya reason hoga ki konsi leads nahi aa pa rahi hai? Aap khol ke dekhiye na ek pure ek mahine se jab bhi main IndiaMART kholta hu no relevant leads found aisa hi aa raha hai.
Executive: Accha haan maine khola tha no relevant by leads found aa raha hai and kis cheez ki aap leads matlab aapke 10 product hai koi bhi aap specific one product aap mujhe name bata sakte ho abhi?
Customer: Kyunki main aapke 10 product hai aap mujhe koi si ek aisi particular product ka lead hai main apne portal pe ek bar check kar leta hu ki abhi hai ya nahi hai.
Executive: Wood sleeper dekh lijiye na.
Executive: Wood sleeper ek second copy karta hu. Aap jab bhi kholte hain tabhi hamesha ye options hi aata hai?
Customer: Haan. Okay.

Executive: Vertical wood sleeper mein sir aap abhi system pe hoge kya?
Customer: Main abhi bahar hu 5-10 minute lagenge mujhe.
Executive: Okay aap 5-10 minute mein system pe baith jao kyunki maine ek lead kholi hai to mujhe dikh rahi hai main aapko wo just aap se confirm karna chah raha hu ki is tarah ki leads aapke kaam ki hai bhi ya nahi hai. Usi hisab se hum system pe kaam kare. Theek hai. Main aapko dobara call karta hu 3:24 hai main teen kitne 10 minute mein aapko karu?
Customer: Hmm 10 minute baad kijiye na.
Executive: Theek hai theek hai.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer is not getting relevant leads.

Resolution:

- Executive checked and found no relevant buyleads.

- Executive asked for a specific product name.

- Executive asked customer to be on system in 10 minutes.



Next Steps: 

- Executive will call back in 10 minutes.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Neutral -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:

- buyleads, product, follow up
